t the infinitive form of an action.\n\n**PROTOCOL 7: THE FILTER (Size Constraint)**\nAll processed words and their roots were longer than a single character, adhering to the size constraint.\n\n**PROTOCOL 8: EXECUTIVE SUMMARY**\nThis summary details the application of each protocol, highlighting specific decisions, corrections, and scholarly guesses made during the processing of the input batch.","input_words":["የሚያስጨንቅም","የሚያስጨንቋትም","የሚያስጨንቋቸውንም","የሚያስጸይፉና","የሚያስጸይፍም","የሚያስፈለልጋቸው","የሚያስፈልጋችሁም","የሚያስፈልግኝ","የሚያስፈሩትንም","የሚያስፈሩኝን","የሚያስፈራህም","የሚያስፈራሩም","የሚያስፈራራቸው","የሚያስፈራራቸውም","የሚያስፈራችሁና","የሚያስፈራንን","የሚያስፈታም","የሚያስፈታን","የሚያስፈጽሙባቸው","የሚያስፈፁሙ","የሚያሸልብበት","የሚያሸክምም","የሚያሸጋገሩ","የሚያሻማቸው","የሚያሻሸል","የሚያሻግሩንን","የሚያሻግርና","የሚያሽቆለቁለው","የሚያሾከሹኩ","የሚያቀልሙበት"],"batch_number":null,"batch_label":null,"model_version":"gemini-2.5-flash"},{"id":"df74772a-52ff-4ffd-8bd3-619aa6bf2fa5","created_at":"2026-03-03T23:13:53.550213+00:00","word":null,"source_file":"rare_words_25/chunk_0230.txt","batch_index":0,"words":[{"pos":"Verb","root":"ማቅረብ","word":"የሚያቀርበት","synonyms":["to present","to offer","to submit","to provide","to bring forth"],"importance":5},{"pos":"Verb","root":"ማቅረብ","word":"የሚያቀርቡላችሁን","synonyms":["to present","to offer","to submit","to provide","to bring forth"],"importance":5},{"pos":"Verb","root":"ማቅረብ","word":"የሚያቀርቡልዎት","synonyms":["to present","to offer","to submit","to provide","to bring forth"],"importance":5},{"pos":"Verb","root":"ማቀበል","word":"የሚያቀብላትን","synonyms":["to hand over","to pass on","to deliver","to transmit"],"importance":5},{"pos":"Verb","root":"ማቀናበር","word":"የሚያቀነነባብሩ","synonyms":["to arrange","to organize","to compose","to coordinate","to compile"],"importance":5},{"pos":"Verb","root":"ማቀናበር","word":"የሚያቀናብረው","synonyms":["to arrange","to organize","to compose","to coordinate","to compile"],"importance":5},{"pos":"Verb","root":"ማቀናበር","word":"የሚያቀናብርልህ","synonyms":["to arrange","to organize","to compose","to coordinate","to compile"],"importance":5},{"pos"